cabal-version:      3.0
name:               aoc2024hs
version:            0.1.0.0
synopsis:           Advent of Code Solutions
-- description:
license:            MIT
license-file:       LICENSE
author:             Lqnk4
maintainer:         internalbeast109@gmail.com
